'''站点可靠性工程'''(Site reliability engineering，SRE)是一门將[[软件工程|软件工程]]应用于[[基础设施|基础设施]]以及运营的学科<ref name="WiseGeek,2020">{{Cite web |url=https://www.wisegeek.com/what-does-a-reliability-engineer-do.htm |title=What Does a Reliability Engineer Do? |access-date=2021-02-11 |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024064719/https://www.wisegeek.com/what-does-a-reliability-engineer-do.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，該概念由[[Google|Google]]於2003年提出<ref>{{cite news |title=SRE vs DevOps：它们有共同点吗？ |url=https://www.uwintech.cn/blog/sre-vs-devops |accessdate=2021-02-11 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116025545/https://www.uwintech.cn/blog/sre-vs-devops |dead-url=no }}</ref>。站点可靠性工程主要目标是创建[[可扩展性|可扩展]]和[[高可用性|高可用性]]的软件系统<ref>[https://techcrunch.com/2016/03/02/are-site-reliability-engineers-the-next-data-scientists Are SRE the next data scientists?] {{Wayback|url=https://techcrunch.com/2016/03/02/are-site-reliability-engineers-the-next-data-scientists |date=20190812094909 }}, [[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]], Mar 2, 2016, Donald Fischer</ref>。

== 職責 ==
站点可靠性工程师的工作上要花50%的时间来參與與軟件運營相关的工作，如解決问题、随叫随到和人工干预。由于站点可靠性工程师所负责的软件系统需要高度自动化和自我修复，所以站点可靠性工程师要将另外50%的时间用于开发工作，如增加新功能等工作<ref>{{Cite magazine|last=Jones|first=Chris|last2=Underwood|first2=Todd|last3=Nukala|first3=Shylaja|date=June 2015|title=Hiring Site Reliability Engineers|url=https://www.usenix.org/system/files/login/articles/login_june_07_jones.pdf|magazine=;login:|volume=40|pages=35-39|access-date=2021-02-11|archive-date=2017-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170824111051/https://www.usenix.org/system/files/login/articles/login_june_07_jones.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

